title: Server transfer down?
body:
I used to play on OCE, I live in Australia. But switched to NA for TFT, with the recent announcement of the other ping dependant games (Project L, the shooter and the mmo thing?), I'd like to switch back to OCE.

When I try to transfer, nothing happens. Is the service not available and if so, when will it

replies.body: having the same problem :( just want to move my account for my holiday :(
